  <brief_title>Study of Administration Of Antithrombin in Patients With Low Plasmatic Levels of Antithrombin After Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <acronym>ATIII</acronym>
  <official_title>Effects of the Administration Of Antithrombin on the Coagulation Status and on the Inflammatory Response in Patients With Low Plasmatic Levels of Antithrombin After Cardiac Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
